2024, what a year!!! 🌱
A year of change, growth, and challenges. 🙌🏻
A year full of lessons, love, and light. 💫

I’m grateful for every little thing—the coffee, the slow mornings, this life, every place I got to visit, the new friendships I made, the amazing people around me, my family, those who always supported me, and the brands that believed in me. 🫂

My heart is so full as this chapter comes to an end. 🥹💞
Here’s to 2025 and all that it has in store. ✨
